WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:23.230 --> 00:00:24.260
Your Highness!

3
00:00:25.190 --> 00:00:28.260
It'll be half a day until we reach the 
location where the monster was sighted.

4
00:00:28.260 --> 00:00:30.500
Yes, I understand.

5
00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:33.470
We've still got some way to 
go, but remain vigilant—

6
00:00:40.820 --> 00:00:42.440
It's here!

7
00:00:46.650 --> 00:00:47.910
That can't be!

8
00:00:47.910 --> 00:00:50.060
The monster came this way to attack us?!

9
00:00:50.060 --> 00:00:52.780
We're not prepared to go into combat!

10
00:00:52.780 --> 00:00:54.520
Looks like we're in luck.

11
00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:55.140
What?!

12
00:00:57.030 --> 00:00:59.400
We've been saved a half-day's 
worth of walking.

13
00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:02.460
It's no use!

14
00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:03.920
This thing's stronger than they said!

15
00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:06.130
W-We can't even get close!

16
00:01:23.020 --> 00:01:27.810
Ex Seque Duel!

17
00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:41.230
A-A single blow!

18
00:01:45.120 --> 00:01:47.040
Your Highness!

19
00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:48.270
Well done, Your Highness!

20
00:01:48.270 --> 00:01:49.380
What fine swordsmanship!

21
00:01:49.380 --> 00:01:51.760
Our princess, and Commander 
of the Third Legion!

22
00:01:51.760 --> 00:01:55.090
Princess! Princess! Princess!

23
00:01:57.340 --> 00:02:00.090
A shout of victory!

24
00:02:00.090 --> 00:02:03.310
Princess! Princess! Princess!

25
00:02:39.310 --> 00:02:43.480
<i>Many moons have passed since the Imperial 
Army went to war with the Hellhorde.</i>

26
00:02:44.050 --> 00:02:48.680
<i>I fell into the hands of the Hellhorde, and 
find myself imprisoned with Her Highness.</i>

27
00:02:48.350 --> 00:02:51.060
Sentient Sacred Blade
Ex

28
00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:54.170
<i>Her Highness has seen her fair share of war,</i>

29
00:02:54.170 --> 00:02:56.220
<i>proving herself on the battlefield 
time and time again.</i>

30
00:02:56.700 --> 00:02:58.810
<i>These indignities are hardly enough...</i>

31
00:03:00.030 --> 00:03:01.710
<i>to break her will!</i>

32
00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.340
Princess.

33
00:03:52.340 --> 00:03:56.620
Is there no way to get you to reveal 
the Royal Empire's secrets?

34
00:03:58.060 --> 00:03:59.220
Save your breath.

35
00:03:59.220 --> 00:04:04.000
Her Highness is not only a princess, but 
Commander of the Imperial Third Legion.

36
00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:07.450
She would not so easily 
divulge imperial secrets.

37
00:04:09.950 --> 00:04:11.300
Is that so?

38
00:04:11.730 --> 00:04:15.030
In that case, though it pains me greatly...

39
00:04:15.420 --> 00:04:19.610
Starting today, we will be subjecting 
you to full-blown torture.

40
00:04:17.310 --> 00:04:21.320
Hellhorde Grand Inquisitor
Torture Tortura

41
00:04:21.870 --> 00:04:22.810
Torture?!

42
00:04:26.750 --> 00:04:27.700
Wait!

43
00:04:27.700 --> 00:04:30.170
War prisoner conventions 
prohibit the use of torture!

44
00:04:30.170 --> 00:04:32.030
Those are human laws, are they not?

45
00:04:32.920 --> 00:04:33.970
Ex.

46
00:04:34.620 --> 00:04:36.420
Don't worry about me.

47
00:04:36.420 --> 00:04:37.300
Your Highness!

48
00:04:37.530 --> 00:04:43.690
Sear me with flames and burn my 
body, but I will keep my silence.

49
00:04:44.920 --> 00:04:46.340
Your Highness.

50
00:04:52.730 --> 00:04:53.990
In that case...

51
00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:57.860
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

52
00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:20.040
What?

53
00:05:34.140 --> 00:05:41.480
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

54
00:06:57.190 --> 00:06:58.670
What in the world?

55
00:07:00.030 --> 00:07:01.270
'Tis toast.

56
00:07:01.490 --> 00:07:02.700
Toast?!

57
00:07:03.590 --> 00:07:06.240
And what exactly do you 
plan to do with <i>that</i>?!

58
00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:08.030
Don't tell me you plan on 
enticing her with food!

59
00:07:08.030 --> 00:07:09.520
She's not a child, you know!

60
00:07:09.890 --> 00:07:11.710
Looks yummy...

61
00:07:12.020 --> 00:07:13.150
Your Highness?

62
00:07:13.790 --> 00:07:15.000
D-Don't get me wrong, Ex!

63
00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:16.880
I'm not feeling tempted at all!

64
00:07:16.880 --> 00:07:18.710
I simply gave my honest impression 
of how good it looks!

65
00:07:18.710 --> 00:07:20.180
All human beings would feel the same way!

66
00:07:20.180 --> 00:07:23.050
So I definitely didn't give 
 in to temptation here...

67
00:07:21.220 --> 00:07:23.050
Slow down!

68
00:07:24.290 --> 00:07:28.500
I would never give in to 
the likes of mere toast!

69
00:07:38.110 --> 00:07:40.370
<i></i><i>Ah, I can see it...</i>

70
00:07:40.720 --> 00:07:42.070
<i></i><i>I can just see it!</i>

71
00:07:42.870 --> 00:07:44.690
<i></i><i>A carpet of gold!</i>

72
00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:47.680
<i></i><i>The heads of wheat, heavy with grain...</i>

73
00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:50.870
<i></i><i>just waiting to be harvested!</i>

74
00:07:53.810 --> 00:07:58.920
<i></i><i>The yeast and unsalted butter 
performing in perfect harmony!</i>

75
00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:06.740
<i></i><i>And most of all, that snow-white angel, 
the flour, with its fragrant aroma!</i>

76
00:08:09.820 --> 00:08:10.620
Your Highness?

77
00:08:11.500 --> 00:08:12.660
You've got it wrong, Ex!

78
00:08:12.660 --> 00:08:13.720
This is, um, you know!

79
00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:14.460
Ah yes! That's it!

80
00:08:14.460 --> 00:08:16.630
What I mean is not what you're thinking!

81
00:08:16.630 --> 00:08:17.580
It's something else entirely!

82
00:08:17.580 --> 00:08:18.420
See, don't you get it now?!

83
00:08:18.420 --> 00:08:19.860
That's what I'm talking about!

84
00:08:18.420 --> 00:08:19.860
Please wipe the drool off your face.

85
00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:21.230
Shh.

86
00:08:34.010 --> 00:08:36.250
<i></i><i>I-I can hear it!</i>

87
00:08:36.250 --> 00:08:37.350
<i></i><i>It sounds...</i>

88
00:08:37.350 --> 00:08:39.120
<i></i><i>It sounds so tasty!</i>

89
00:08:39.450 --> 00:08:42.050
<i></i><i>The crunchy, flame-seared surface.</i>

90
00:08:42.050 --> 00:08:44.610
<i></i><i>A little burnt, which only makes it better!</i>

91
00:08:44.970 --> 00:08:49.930
<i></i><i>As it's torn open, it refuses to stay 
silent and emits those dulcet tones!</i>

92
00:08:54.170 --> 00:08:57.410
<i></i><i>And its chewy, moist interior!</i>

93
00:08:59.050 --> 00:09:00.460
<i></i><i>Thank you!</i>

94
00:09:00.460 --> 00:09:03.450
<i></i><i>Thank you, tasty sounds!</i>

95
00:09:05.000 --> 00:09:08.520
<i></i><i>A hearty meal for the ears!</i>

96
00:09:09.690 --> 00:09:10.960
Your Highness?

97
00:09:13.620 --> 00:09:14.630
Your Highness!

98
00:09:15.330 --> 00:09:16.390
Curses...

99
00:09:16.900 --> 00:09:22.650
I am Commander of the Imperial Third Legion.

100
00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:26.420
I-I will never give in...

101
00:09:27.060 --> 00:09:28.960
to your pathetic torture!

102
00:09:29.970 --> 00:09:32.350
The torture isn't over yet.

103
00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:36.850
'Tis a bowl of beef stew 
that has been eaten.

104
00:09:36.850 --> 00:09:37.960
You wouldn't dare!

105
00:09:38.310 --> 00:09:39.710
You fiend!

106
00:09:45.750 --> 00:09:49.570
That <i>has</i> to taste amazing!

107
00:10:27.920 --> 00:10:30.810
I'll talk...

108
00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:33.680
I see.

109
00:10:34.190 --> 00:10:36.610
So that's the weak point 
of the Imperial Army.

110
00:10:37.350 --> 00:10:38.450
Your Highness...

111
00:10:39.670 --> 00:10:42.210
It appears to be reliable information.

112
00:10:42.210 --> 00:10:43.610
I did it.

113
00:10:43.610 --> 00:10:45.020
I spilled the beans.

114
00:10:45.370 --> 00:10:48.860
So let me have some toast.

115
00:10:48.860 --> 00:10:50.490
Just one slice.

116
00:10:50.490 --> 00:10:52.990
One slice is all I ask for!

117
00:10:52.990 --> 00:10:54.030
One slice?

118
00:10:54.640 --> 00:10:56.270
What are you saying?

119
00:10:56.270 --> 00:10:59.440
You've already divulged your secrets.

120
00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:02.000
In other words, we're done with you.

121
00:11:03.930 --> 00:11:05.570
You won't get just one slice...

122
00:11:06.700 --> 00:11:08.950
We'll throw a toast party!

123
00:11:08.950 --> 00:11:10.820
Yay!

124
00:11:11.270 --> 00:11:13.270
What..?

125
00:11:15.980 --> 00:11:18.600
So yummy!

126
00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:22.430
Untz, untz, untz!

127
00:11:22.080 --> 00:11:25.740
Untz, untz, untz...

128
00:11:22.430 --> 00:11:25.740
Untz, untz, untz!

129
00:11:25.830 --> 00:11:28.750
Grand 
Inquisitor's
 Chamber

130
00:11:27.390 --> 00:11:28.740
What was that?

131
00:11:29.050 --> 00:11:33.400
Our army is too feeble to win 
with a meager secret like that?

132
00:11:33.650 --> 00:11:34.670
Yes.

133
00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:36.290
<i>Understood.</i>

134
00:11:36.850 --> 00:11:39.810
We will delay the princess's release

135
00:11:39.810 --> 00:11:42.230
until I obtain information 
that our army can use.

136
00:11:45.890 --> 00:11:49.130
Don't take it personally, Princess.

137
00:11:50.260 --> 00:11:54.150
I'm doing this all for 
the sake of His Majesty.

138
00:11:54.940 --> 00:12:01.040
Starting today, the princess will 
be tortured on a daily basis.

139
00:12:04.200 --> 00:12:07.030
'Tis Time for "Torture," Princess

140
00:12:11.390 --> 00:12:14.760
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

141
00:12:18.440 --> 00:12:22.140
Grand Inquisitor Torture Tortura.

142
00:12:23.380 --> 00:12:27.010
Her Highness may have been bested 
yesterday due to her hunger,

143
00:12:27.010 --> 00:12:30.880
but thanks to your bread torture from 
yesterday, she's all <i>bread</i>y today!

144
00:12:31.140 --> 00:12:32.300
As in, full of bread!

145
00:12:33.320 --> 00:12:35.620
Today's the day that Her Highness,

146
00:12:35.620 --> 00:12:38.230
Princess and Commander of 
the Imperial Third Legion,

147
00:12:38.230 --> 00:12:40.180
stands up to your torture!

148
00:12:40.450 --> 00:12:43.950
Yes, no matter what you 
may subject her to...

149
00:12:42.190 --> 00:12:44.280
Takoyaki

150
00:12:42.190 --> 00:12:44.280
Sauce

151
00:12:42.190 --> 00:12:44.280
Cheese

152
00:12:42.190 --> 00:12:44.280
Extra-Spicy 
Sauce

153
00:12:52.990 --> 00:12:55.140
Takoyaki?

154
00:12:55.890 --> 00:12:57.530
Don't kid me with that takoyaki!

155
00:12:57.530 --> 00:13:00.810
Like I said, Her Highness 
is all <i>bread</i>y for you!

156
00:13:01.610 --> 00:13:04.990
Besides, Her Highness was 
raised on the finest meals,

157
00:13:04.990 --> 00:13:08.840
so she'd never be done in 
by such low-brow food!

158
00:13:08.600 --> 00:13:10.850
Takoyaki

159
00:13:08.600 --> 00:13:10.850
Sauce

160
00:13:08.600 --> 00:13:10.850
Cheese

161
00:13:08.600 --> 00:13:10.850
Extra-Spicy 
Sauce

162
00:13:08.840 --> 00:13:10.070
Your Highness?

163
00:13:10.840 --> 00:13:12.470
Th-That's right!

164
00:13:12.470 --> 00:13:16.350
You can't sway me with something 
I've never eaten, like takoyaki!

165
00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:21.770
I know what it is, at least.

166
00:13:21.900 --> 00:13:24.820
Takoyaki

167
00:13:21.900 --> 00:13:24.820
Crêpes

168
00:13:21.900 --> 00:13:24.820
Yakisoba

169
00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:27.380
I'd always gaze out of the palace 
windows alone at the festivals.

170
00:13:28.860 --> 00:13:31.250
The citizens bought them from stalls...

171
00:13:31.590 --> 00:13:35.150
to eat with family! Lovers! Friends!

172
00:13:35.500 --> 00:13:37.880
With smiles on their faces!

173
00:13:41.470 --> 00:13:45.140
H-Honestly, I was so jealous of them...

174
00:13:45.830 --> 00:13:46.640
She's crying!

175
00:13:47.800 --> 00:13:48.820
Princess.

176
00:13:50.140 --> 00:13:51.670
Would you like to try one?

177
00:13:52.960 --> 00:13:54.610
You mustn't, Your Highness!

178
00:13:55.340 --> 00:13:58.710
If you stuff your face with 
freshly-made takoyaki...

179
00:14:00.090 --> 00:14:01.900
Your Highness!

180
00:14:05.890 --> 00:14:07.400
But she looks happy!

181
00:14:07.400 --> 00:14:08.520
<i>Yum!</i>

182
00:14:08.620 --> 00:14:09.640
<i>Yum!</i>

183
00:14:09.740 --> 00:14:10.860
<i>Yum!</i>

184
00:14:10.960 --> 00:14:23.300
<i>Yum!</i>

185
00:14:23.300 --> 00:14:25.330
<i></i><i>Crispy on the outside!</i>

186
00:14:23.300 --> 00:14:37.400
<i>Yum!</i>

187
00:14:25.330 --> 00:14:27.340
<i></i><i>Gooey on the inside!</i>

188
00:14:27.720 --> 00:14:30.440
<i></i><i>Plump octopus right in the middle...</i>

189
00:14:34.000 --> 00:14:35.170
<i></i><i>Mingling!</i>

190
00:14:35.660 --> 00:14:39.150
<i></i><i>The octopus and batter mingling 
as they dance in your mouth!</i>

191
00:14:40.800 --> 00:14:43.090
<i></i><i>The way it asserts itself as 
it passes down your throat!</i>

192
00:14:43.090 --> 00:14:45.670
<i></i><i>Its faint warmth even as 
it reaches your stomach!</i>

193
00:14:46.780 --> 00:14:49.640
<i></i><i>A carnival of joy in every bodily organ!</i>

194
00:14:52.020 --> 00:14:53.270
<i></i><i>So this is...</i>

195
00:14:54.110 --> 00:14:55.820
<i></i><i>T-A-K-O-yaki!</i>

196
00:14:55.790 --> 00:14:58.750
Truly

197
00:14:56.410 --> 00:14:58.750
Ambrosial

198
00:14:56.790 --> 00:14:58.750
Kaleidoscope of

199
00:14:57.290 --> 00:14:58.750
Octopus

200
00:14:59.580 --> 00:15:02.080
The princess 
confessed

201
00:15:03.340 --> 00:15:04.680
I see.

202
00:15:05.100 --> 00:15:08.920
So that's where the Imperial 
Army hid its ultimate weapon.

203
00:15:10.710 --> 00:15:11.840
Take a look, Ex!

204
00:15:12.300 --> 00:15:14.620
I grilled this one myself!

205
00:15:14.620 --> 00:15:16.000
There's cheese inside!

206
00:15:16.730 --> 00:15:19.020
Crispy and gooey! Plump and gooey!

207
00:15:16.730 --> 00:15:19.020
Crispy and gooey... Plump and gooey...

208
00:15:19.600 --> 00:15:22.020
Grand 
Inquisitor's
 Chamber

209
00:15:20.780 --> 00:15:22.020
Excuse me?

210
00:15:22.490 --> 00:15:23.760
His Majesty said what?

211
00:15:25.010 --> 00:15:26.270
That's right.

212
00:15:25.610 --> 00:15:28.280
Attendant to the Hell-Lord

213
00:15:25.610 --> 00:15:28.280
Kanadge

214
00:15:29.690 --> 00:15:34.510
He said, "I'm too scared to 
use a weapon that powerful."

215
00:15:38.780 --> 00:15:40.120
I see.

216
00:15:40.450 --> 00:15:42.830
I suppose that's that if he's scared.

217
00:15:42.830 --> 00:15:45.050
I shall have to come up 
with a different torture.

218
00:15:46.830 --> 00:15:48.870
'Tis quite late already.

219
00:15:48.870 --> 00:15:50.500
I must retire for the night soon.

220
00:15:51.250 --> 00:15:52.720
That's it!

221
00:15:54.300 --> 00:15:56.720
The Next Day, 
Midnight

222
00:15:58.030 --> 00:16:01.090
'Tis time for torture, Princess.

223
00:16:01.090 --> 00:16:03.430
Torture this late at night?

224
00:16:03.430 --> 00:16:05.520
Does the Hellhorde know no manners?

225
00:16:05.520 --> 00:16:07.380
I do apologize.

226
00:16:07.380 --> 00:16:10.750
However, I chose this time for a reason.

227
00:16:11.850 --> 00:16:13.560
I've got it, Ex.

228
00:16:13.560 --> 00:16:16.250
She must plan on using sleep 
deprivation to torture me.

229
00:16:16.250 --> 00:16:17.630
I see!

230
00:16:17.630 --> 00:16:20.750
It's true that sleep deprivation would 
be excruciating for the average person.

231
00:16:21.350 --> 00:16:26.210
However, Your Highness is Princess and 
Commander of the Imperial Third Legion.

232
00:16:26.590 --> 00:16:29.040
You've faced fierce battlefields 
with no room to rest,

233
00:16:29.040 --> 00:16:32.290
fighting for nights on end without sleep.

234
00:16:32.290 --> 00:16:33.310
Yeah.

235
00:16:33.310 --> 00:16:35.890
I also pulled four all-nighters in 
a row once playing video games.

236
00:16:35.890 --> 00:16:37.590
You can leave that part out!

237
00:16:37.880 --> 00:16:40.520
Anyway, I'm used to going without sleep!

238
00:16:40.520 --> 00:16:42.630
I can handle however 
many hours you throw at me!

239
00:16:42.630 --> 00:16:47.600
Unfortunately, Princess, today's torture 
does not involve depriving you of sleep.

240
00:16:47.600 --> 00:16:48.390
What?

241
00:16:53.960 --> 00:16:56.100
This smell! This warmth!

242
00:16:56.100 --> 00:16:58.870
This devastating power!

243
00:17:00.220 --> 00:17:02.790
S-Surely you wouldn't!

244
00:17:02.790 --> 00:17:04.590
Not this late at night!

245
00:17:07.530 --> 00:17:09.590
Ramen?!

246
00:17:09.590 --> 00:17:11.330
<i>Growl...</i>

247
00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:11.090
Growl

248
00:17:12.030 --> 00:17:14.310
<i></i><i>My stomach was getting ready to go to sleep,</i>

249
00:17:14.310 --> 00:17:17.650
<i></i><i>but it's bolted awake from the visual 
stimulation and smell of the ramen!</i>

250
00:17:17.650 --> 00:17:20.760
<i></i><i>My stomach is like an 
excited little kid now!</i>

251
00:17:18.890 --> 00:17:22.850
Stomach

252
00:17:20.760 --> 00:17:22.840
Gimme that ramen!

253
00:17:22.840 --> 00:17:24.330
You mustn't, Your Highness!

254
00:17:24.330 --> 00:17:25.260
Take a closer look!

255
00:17:25.750 --> 00:17:27.840
That's not just any ramen!

256
00:17:27.840 --> 00:17:29.870
That rich and creamy ramen broth!

257
00:17:30.190 --> 00:17:33.040
Eating that this late at 
night is bad for you!

258
00:17:33.040 --> 00:17:34.390
You'll upset your stomach!

259
00:17:35.040 --> 00:17:37.870
Ex, I know all too well...

260
00:17:38.280 --> 00:17:41.060
How criminal it is to eat ramen 
in the middle of the night.

261
00:17:41.450 --> 00:17:42.580
How stupid it is.

262
00:17:42.930 --> 00:17:44.780
The inevitable guilt.

263
00:17:46.030 --> 00:17:49.020
That's what makes it taste so good!

264
00:17:49.020 --> 00:17:49.790
Your Highness!

265
00:17:50.100 --> 00:17:51.090
'Tis time to eat.

266
00:18:03.880 --> 00:18:07.660
I want some!

267
00:18:05.930 --> 00:18:07.660
Stay strong, Your Highness!

268
00:18:22.530 --> 00:18:23.570
Your Highness!

269
00:18:23.890 --> 00:18:25.250
Your Highness!

270
00:18:25.250 --> 00:18:27.660
Y-Y-Your Highness!

271
00:18:27.660 --> 00:18:29.920
Y-Y-Your...

272
00:18:32.860 --> 00:18:34.200
Kill me now.

273
00:18:34.200 --> 00:18:35.170
Seriously?

274
00:18:35.690 --> 00:18:38.260
Your Highness, have a little patience.

275
00:18:38.260 --> 00:18:40.220
Ramen is a meal enjoyed quickly.

276
00:18:40.220 --> 00:18:42.630
Which means the torture shouldn't last long.

277
00:18:42.630 --> 00:18:44.690
Y-You're right, Ex.

278
00:18:45.390 --> 00:18:49.030
Besides, I've gotten used to 
the ramen's impact.

279
00:18:49.030 --> 00:18:50.690
I'll tough it out.

280
00:18:51.800 --> 00:18:54.160
I will never give in!

281
00:18:55.240 --> 00:18:56.290
What?!

282
00:18:56.700 --> 00:18:58.300
A small bowl of rice?!

283
00:18:58.300 --> 00:18:59.450
Y-You fiend!

284
00:18:59.450 --> 00:19:01.500
Just what are you planning?!

285
00:19:02.020 --> 00:19:05.430
Topping that piping hot rice with 
chili bean paste and garlic,

286
00:19:05.430 --> 00:19:08.610
and wrapping it up in the nori 
that's soaked up the ramen broth!

287
00:19:10.130 --> 00:19:12.510
She ate it!

288
00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:15.590
Your Highness?

289
00:19:16.100 --> 00:19:18.000
Y-Y-Your Highness?!

290
00:19:19.520 --> 00:19:20.550
Your Highness!

291
00:19:20.910 --> 00:19:25.480
Firm noodles, extra dashi, 
spinach topping...

292
00:19:25.480 --> 00:19:27.890
She's putting in an order 
while turning white as ash!

293
00:19:29.020 --> 00:19:31.270
The princess 
confessed

294
00:19:35.560 --> 00:19:37.890
Delish!

295
00:19:40.620 --> 00:19:45.780
It's almost closing time, so these scrap 
ends of pork chashu are on the house.

296
00:19:45.780 --> 00:19:47.350
Awesome!

297
00:19:47.350 --> 00:19:51.460
This is the best part of eating at late-night
 ramen shops right before they close!

298
00:19:52.180 --> 00:19:54.680
We're in a prison cell.

299
00:19:57.430 --> 00:19:58.980
Well?

300
00:19:59.260 --> 00:20:03.700
Was His Majesty pleased with the 
secret I brought him today?

301
00:20:04.120 --> 00:20:04.970
What?

302
00:20:05.370 --> 00:20:06.490
Ah...

303
00:20:06.490 --> 00:20:08.260
Yes, as always.

304
00:20:08.850 --> 00:20:09.800
Yes.

305
00:20:09.800 --> 00:20:11.330
I'll do my best tomorrow.

306
00:20:14.750 --> 00:20:16.540
Grand Inquisitor.

307
00:20:17.560 --> 00:20:21.980
Why don't you leave tomorrow's 
torture session to us?

308
00:20:22.670 --> 00:20:24.230
You two!

309
00:20:30.230 --> 00:20:35.090
Bread... Takoyaki... Ramen...

310
00:20:39.180 --> 00:20:41.180
<i></i><i>Flour is so great!</i>

311
00:20:41.800 --> 00:20:43.530
<i></i><i>The greatest!</i>

312
00:22:19.110 --> 00:22:20.940
It's here!

313
00:22:22.400 --> 00:22:23.530
That can't be!

314
00:22:23.530 --> 00:22:25.730
The monster came this way to attack us?!

315
00:22:25.730 --> 00:22:28.410
We're not prepared to go into combat!

316
00:22:28.410 --> 00:22:30.120
Looks like we're in luck.

317
00:22:30.120 --> 00:22:30.790
What?!

318
00:22:32.760 --> 00:22:35.070
We've been saved a half-day's 
worth of walking.

319
00:22:35.880 --> 00:22:38.740
<i>I can go home early and play video games!</i>

320
00:22:41.780 --> 00:22:45.420
<i>After I save that character, should 
I tackle the Blazing Dungeon?</i>

321
00:22:45.680 --> 00:22:48.510
<i>No, there was that subquest 
that caught my eye.</i>

322
00:22:48.110 --> 00:22:52.420
Ex Seque Duel!

323
00:22:48.510 --> 00:22:50.920
<i>I might be able to get 
a rare item out of it!</i>

324
00:22:50.920 --> 00:22:52.760
<i>That definitely comes first!</i>

325
00:23:05.530 --> 00:23:07.310
Your Highness!

326
00:23:08.250 --> 00:23:11.830
<i>All that sudden movement after drinking 
water gave me a stitch on my side.</i>

327
00:23:12.090 --> 00:23:13.650
<i>It hurts like hell.</i>

328
00:23:13.650 --> 00:23:16.550
<i>So much pain, but everyone's looking at me.</i>

329
00:23:16.870 --> 00:23:20.140
<i>I can't let them know I have a side stitch.</i>

330
00:23:20.140 --> 00:23:21.910
<i>It'd affect the soldiers' morale.</i>

331
00:23:22.420 --> 00:23:23.290
<i>I know.</i>

332
00:23:23.600 --> 00:23:27.210
<i>I heard that stretching can help the pain.</i>

333
00:23:29.670 --> 00:23:32.420
A shout of victory!

334
00:23:32.420 --> 00:23:38.880
Princess! Princess! Princess!

335
00:23:33.660 --> 00:23:38.660
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

336
00:23:34.020 --> 00:23:35.110
<i>Nope.</i>

337
00:23:36.330 --> 00:23:38.660
<i>Stretching doesn't stop 
it from hurting like hell.</i>

